### 1. Criar tarefa
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Estudar Spring Boot",
  "description": "Finalizar projeto To-Do List",
  "completed": false
}

### 2. Criar outra tarefa
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Fazer exercícios",
  "description": "30 minutos de caminhada",
  "completed": false
}

### 3. Listar todas as tarefas
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks

### 4. Buscar tarefa por ID
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1

### 5. Filtrar apenas tarefas concluídas
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks?completed=true

### 6. Filtrar tarefas pendentes
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks?completed=false

### 7. Atualizar tarefa (marcar como concluída)
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Estudar Spring Boot",
  "description": "Finalizar projeto To-Do List",
  "completed": true
}

### 8. Deletar tarefa
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/2

### 9. Buscar ID inexistente (testa o erro 404)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/tasks/999

### 10. Criar tarefa inválida (testa validação)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "AB",
  "description": ""
}